Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.exceptions

  • Exception Summary
    Exception Description
    AlreadyActivatedLeaderCardException
    Exception class invoked when the user ties to activate a leader card already activated
    AlreadyDiscardedLeaderCardException
    Exception class invoked when the user tries to activate or discard a leader card that has been already discarded
    BadInputFormatException
    Exception class invoked when the input is of an incorrect format
    EmptyDeckException
    Exception class invoked when the user tries to bring a card from an empty slot
    EmptySlotException
    Exception class invoked when a card slot is empty
    IllegalInsertionException
    Exception class invoked when specified insertion in warehouse is not permitted
    IllegalMoveException
    Exception class invoked when an illegal move inside warehouse is tried by the user
    InsufficientResourcesException
    Exception class invoked when resources are insufficient to buy a specified item
    MaxPlayersException
    Exception class invoked when more someone tries to add more than four players to the multiplayer game
    PlayerNotExistsException
    Exception class invoked when a player doesn't exists
    StorageOutOfBoundsException
    Exception class invoked when the specified storage index is out of bounds
    WrongCardTypeException
    Exception class invoked when a leader card method is invoked on the wrong leader card type
